Titolo: H.A.T.E.: Hostile All-Terrain Encounter

Anno: 1989

Descrizione: H.A.T.E.: Hostile All-Terrain Encounter is an isometric scrolling shoot 'em up similar to Sega's Zaxxon, developed by Vortex Software and released in 1989 for Commodore 64, ZX Spectrum, Amstrad CPC, Amiga, and Atari ST. The player can choose to play with either an airplane or a tank.